  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink257-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirival eṉṟa talaimakaṟkut tōḻi uṭaṉpaṭātu kūṟiyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante said, not agreeing, to the hero who said, “I will separate after the time of marriage has been fixed.”   
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink257">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavaṉ kaṭavuṭ pēṇi</l>
<l>yirantaṉaṉ peṟṟa velvaḷaik kuṟumaka</l>
<l>ḷāyari neṭuṅkaṇ kaliḻac</l>
<l>cēyttāṟ ṟeyyanī piriyu nāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The land</l>
        <l>to which you depart—</l>
        <l rend="space indent">for the beautiful, red-streaked long eyes</l>
        <l rend="indent">of the small woman</l>
        <l rend="indent">with lustrous bangles</l>
        <l rend="indent">to weep—</l>
        <l rend="indent2">[that woman]</l>
        <l rend="indent2">whom the man, [her father], the hill-dweller,</l>
        <l rend="indent2">who cherished and supplicated the god,</l>
        <l rend="indent2">obtained—</l>
        <l rend="space">alas—</l>
        <l>is far!</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
